Rating: 4
This is a great husband pleaser. I added 1/2 chopped onion, one chopped garlic clove and about 1 1/2 cups cooked, cubed chicken. For the cheese, I used equal amounts of mozzarella and cheddar. I cooked it at 350 degrees for one hour, then topped it with a little additional cheese and cooked until melted. Delish!

